        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Rain suspended mid-air, river lights refusing to sleep, and glass gardens humming after dark.]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<section class="hero_iJHu"><div class="heroText_eEPN"><h2>Singapore · Water &amp; Light</h2><p></p><p>雨幕自穹顶倾泻，河水裹挟霓虹缓缓回旋。
我循着湿润而鲜明的线索，徐行在这座城市。<br>
每一帧都维持原初的呼吸节奏，只轻轻调校色彩，
将南洋的水汽同盛夏一并封存。</p><p></p><p class="meta_KtQk"></p><p>Shot on Apple iPhone 16 Pro · 24&nbsp;mm f/1.78 &amp; 120&nbsp;mm f/2.8<br>
July&nbsp;8-10,&nbsp;2025 · Singapore, SG</p><p></p></div></section>
<section class="gallery_uaBf"><div class="column_ZTVD"><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/jewelImage-1eaabf35d555f8f47df46a26f5cfda86.jpeg" alt="Rain vortex inside Jewel Changi Airport"><figcaption><strong>樟宜机场 · Jewel Changi Airport</strong> · <!-- -->雨漩涡宛若悬自天穹的水晶沙漏，时差与旅途都在此延缓。</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/cityHallImage-842c6d06f3caf5eac251e417b0bd5ffa.jpeg" alt="Parliament House facade glowing after dusk"><figcaption><strong>新加坡国会大厦 · Parliament House</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/cliffordPierImage-e0f882c05cc9130d2adacf017116b93f.jpeg" alt="Clifford Pier illuminated columns at night"><figcaption><strong>克利福德码头 · Clifford Pier</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/chinatownImage-a83f4d973d27632a28bf97b908e72318.jpeg" alt="Chinatown shophouse corridor with hanging lanterns"><figcaption><strong>牛车水 · Chinatown</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/gardensByBayImage-e8f8488b876e8e27e9f480c1ca0d014c.jpg" alt="Supertree Grove lit up at Gardens by the Bay"><figcaption><strong>滨海湾花园 · Gardens by the Bay</strong> · <!-- -->超级树在夜里拔地而起，紫蓝色的光谱为旅程落下帷幕。</figcaption></figure></div><div class="column_ZTVD"><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/clarkeQuayImage-2333f9bc7a6c17e30aca097fda898191.jpeg" alt="Boats passing under Clarke Quay bridge at night"><figcaption><strong>克拉码头 · Clarke Quay</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/nationalGalleryImage-987aa0b21e97c7c16e4d51830d6f1050.jpeg" alt="Victoria Concert Hall clock tower glowing after dusk"><figcaption><strong>维多利亚音乐厅 · Victoria Concert Hall</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/merlionImage-e3eb8b7e89df293db0c05bdafa13aa84.jpeg" alt="Merlion statue spraying water toward Marina Bay"><figcaption><strong>鱼尾狮 · Merlion</strong> · </figcaption></figure><figure><img src="https://jerrylinyx.github.io/Doc/assets/images/floralFantasyImage-9ff70d2eba72942b419b35ef11b02aba.jpeg" alt="Marina Bay Sands skyline reflecting on Marina Bay"><figcaption><strong>滨海湾金沙酒店 · Marina Bay Sands</strong> · </figcaption></figure></div></section>
<section class="footerNote_T72d"><h2>Behind the Frame</h2><p></p><p>若你也想感受狮城的脉搏，可以从午后的克拉码头启程，沿着新加坡河走到滨海湾——流水和光影会替你规划好每一幕。</p><p></p></section>]]></content>
